{"tid":1029571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六千多名非本地畢業生留港就業獲居留權","createTime":"2019-02-20T10:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T16:04:42.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"58953f62a8f74ac6de02a71e4628dc632b1d4819","tid":1029571,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】保安局文件顯示，過去三年共有六千多人，透過非本地畢業生留港或回港就業安排計劃，取得香港的居留權。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行計劃，非本地學生在香港修讀學士學位或更高資歷課程，畢業後六個月內可以申請留港尋找工作，或者六個月後獲得聘用，申請回港工作。<br />\n<br />\n保安局文件顯示，過去三年因為參與以上計劃獲得香港居留權的人數逐年上升，2016年有1979人、2017年有2172人，增加至去年有2455人，保安局未有提供當中多少是內地人。<br />\n<br />\n而去年有關計劃的申請人數就有10200多宗，當中逾九成八獲批，超過九成是內地人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去三年有超過11000名內地學生以留港就學為理由，申請延期逗留。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=338238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338238&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n829Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=ea16e308\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338238&h=893decfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=338238</a>"},{"pid":"99a3c89b63d10c5e3a96d681214184bce922a83e","tid":1029571,"uid":93986,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:29:56.000Z","msg":"通街派，香港政府我屌你老母"},{"pid":"deca7cc80a890a2395c1ffd7d8912dd309188b10","tid":1029571,"uid":7343,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"而家啲工請哂支那狗 <br />\n本地人就嚟失哂業"},{"pid":"f24d7a084d6bf32f27702a7dc83ffd81fdb2e9e0","tid":1029571,"uid":114946,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"八大學店垃圾taught master收大把中國野雞。<br />\n十幾萬買香港身份證，抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffb769aceb54309fe0dc33c7745a9a37db6cfed","tid":1029571,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"有錢人都可以做香港人<